{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511780/extras/Pose_carte.gif?t=1737560628\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Vestiges: Fallen Tribes</i></strong> is a card game mixed with an autobattler, compatible with PC and VR, and set in a tribal science-fiction universe. Build the deck representing your tribe, manipulate your figurines and place them on the battlefield. Soldiers automatically fight until one of the armies is decimated. Use strategy to defeat your opponents!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511780/extras/1_05_solo_missions.png?t=1737560628\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Overcome predefined solo missions and weekly challenges and learn more about the story of this dystopian world.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511780/extras/1_07_deckbuilding.png?t=1737560628\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build a powerful deck of 20 cards by combining units from your favorite tribe. Which of the Adrariis or the Illustrans will you choose to stand by ?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511780/extras/1_08_pvp.png?t=1737560628\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Turn by turn, the positioning of your units will be key. Reflection will be your ally to anticipate the movements of your enemies, in this game with accessible and infinitely replayable gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511780/extras/1_10_tribal.png?t=1737560628\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Compete against your opponents for control of the most precious resource: water. Clans, tribes, ancient civilizations, they all need it to survive on a planet turned into a desert by human exploitation. Your battlefield will be this new world built on the vestiges of the old one.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Adrarii recruit ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2511780/ecf55f266710ddeaeacd0b9349252e82c3c5dbfa.jpg"},{"name":"Illustran recruit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2511780/7ebfcc608353e023e6bf5cd639a858f8ab12c528.jpg"},{"name":"Perfect Victory ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2511780/2e8ca37d8ce6da9ae40daecf1cc7806b4d84b2c3.jpg"},{"name":"The perforator ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2511780/47825595cf9272c4df8a712a6d2cc9f1f40f6017.jpg"},{"name":"The Goat ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2511780/ea4f9349f83d292d0cf49fab43df7931e9557faf.jpg"},{"name":"The Wolf\u2019s child ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2511780/795fc55aba6e6ba9dc22d66cc15ab556362e1a1b.jpg"},{"name":"I made my own story ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2511780/327b7bbd7c1ae7fdb18d146355d7a3e149b3c9ec.jpg"},{"name":"I survived Arwhii ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2511780/c1edba6d96ed0fb3cf08b233e42d804c9f42ed5e.jpg"},{"name":"I survived Matria ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2511780/5f2de00d62454e6e90a278238bdd911884f0a84d.jpg"},{"name":"More water please ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2511780/5a4aa2d7422895451fbe178